            "id": "688b740f09622700019c0313",
            "title": "Wall Street&#39;s Most Accurate Analysts Spotlight On 3 Financial Stocks Delivering High-Dividend Yields",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-dhlHIi fuaxyy\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">During times of turbulence and uncertainty in the markets, many investors turn to dividend-yielding stocks. These are often companies that have high free cash flows and reward shareholders with a<a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/yield-investments\" target=\"_blank\"> high dividend payout</a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Benzinga readers can review the latest analyst takes on their favorite stocks by visiting <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-stock-ratings\" target=\"_blank\">Analyst Stock Ratings</a> page. Traders can sort through Benzinga's extensive database of analyst ratings, including <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/analyst-color/22/09/28888638/exclusive-study-finds-benzinga-analyst-ratings-data-yields-market-beating-strategie\" target=\"_blank\">by analyst accuracy</a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Below are the ratings of the most accurate analysts for three high-yielding stocks in the financial sector.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-hmmYps csiXRL\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold\">Trending Investment Opportunities</div><div class=\"flex items-end justify-end\"><div class=\"text-right text-sm bg-gray-200 rounded px-2 py-1\">Advertisement</div></div></div></div><div class=\"cta-stacked GalleryCarousel_splide_slidewrap__zHpTC\"><div class=\"sc-cwcSVF hlcLHF carousel-container\"><div aria-label=\"Carousel\" class=\"splide\"><div class=\"splide-track-wrapper\"><div class=\"splide__track\"><ul class=\"splide__list\"><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"carousel-pagination\"><div class=\"splide__arrows\"><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev page-left-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M15 239c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9L207 465c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0s9.4-24.6 0-33.9L65.9 256 241 81c9.4-9.4 9.4-24.6 0-33.9s-24.6-9.4-33.9 0L15 239z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--next page-right-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M305 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L113 465c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0s-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l175-175L79 81c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9s24.6-9.4 33.9 0L305 239z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>WhiteHorse Finance, Inc. <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"WHF\" style=\"display:inline-block\">WHF</span></strong></h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Dividend Yield:</strong> 17.72%</li>\n<li><strong>Raymond James </strong>analyst Robert Dodd downgraded the stock from Outperform to Market Perform on Nov. 8, 2024. This analyst has an accuracy rate of 63%.</li>\n<li><strong>JP Morgan </strong>analyst Richard Shane maintained an Underweight rating and cut the price target from $12.5 to $11.5 on July 29, 2024. This analyst has an accuracy rate of 67%.</li>\n<li><strong>Recent News:</strong> WhiteHorse Finance will release its second quarter financial results on Thursday, Aug. 7.</li>\n<li>Benzinga Pro’s real-time newsfeed alerted to latest WHF <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/pro/register?utm_adType=bzprocontent&amp;utm_campaign=14daytrial&amp;utm_ad=0731\" target=\"_blank\">news</a>. </li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Ellington Credit Company <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"EARN\" style=\"display:inline-block\">EARN</span></strong></h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Dividend Yield:</strong> 16.30%</li>\n<li><strong>UBS </strong>analyst Douglas Harter maintained a Neutral rating and raised the price target from $5.5 to $5.75 on July 16, 2025. This analyst has an accuracy rate of 69%.</li>\n<li><strong>JMP Securities </strong>analyst Mikhail Goberman reiterated a Market Perform rating on April 19, 2024. This analyst has an accuracy rate of 74%.</li>\n<li><strong>Recent News:</strong> On May 20, Ellington Credit posted downbeat quarterly earnings.</li>\n<li>Benzinga Pro's real-time newsfeed alerted to <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/pro/register?utm_adType=bzprocontent&amp;utm_campaign=14daytrial&amp;utm_ad=0731\" target=\"_blank\">latest EARN news</a> </li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Two Harbors Investment Corp. <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"TWO\" style=\"display:inline-block\">TWO</span></strong></h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Dividend Yield: </strong>17.66%</li>\n<li><strong>UBS </strong>analyst Douglas Harter maintained a Buy rating and cut the price target from $13 to $12 on July 10, 2025. This analyst has an accuracy rate of 69%.</li>\n<li><strong>RBC Capital </strong>analyst Kenneth Lee maintained a Sector Perform rating and cut the price target from $13 to $12 on May 28, 2025. This analyst has an accuracy rate of 68%.</li>\n<li><strong>Recent News: </strong>On July 28, the company posted downbeat quarterly earnings.</li>\n<li>Benzinga Pro’s real-time newsfeed alerted to latest TWO <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/pro/register?utm_adType=bzprocontent&amp;utm_campaign=14daytrial&amp;utm_ad=0731\" target=\"_blank\">news </a></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-46757288\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/trading-ideas/short-ideas/25/07/46756402/top-2-risk-off-stocks-that-may-keep-you-up-at-night-this-month\" target=\"_blank\">Top 2 Risk Off Stocks That May Keep You Up At Night This Month</a></strong></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Photo via Shutterstock</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-dGJnDi fsipWW\"></div><!--/$--></div></div>",
